<div id="content">

<p>Welcome to my website. As you may have guessed from the
text above, I work in the <a href=
"http://www.cs.st-andrews.ac.uk">School of Computer Science</a> at
the <a href="http://www.st-andrews.ac.uk">University of St
Andrews</a> in Scotland. Please browse the links to find out more
about me and what I do, or take a look at my <a href=
"research/pubs.php">papers</a>. Or here are some ways to <a href=
"about/contact.php">reach me</a>.</p>

<hr />

<h3>Notices</h3>

<ul>

<li>We have a new baby girl!</li>

<li>New research project: <a href="http://www.pvnets.org">Privacy
Value Networks</a>.</li>

<li>New funded PhD opportunities in <a 
href="http://www.cs.st-andrews.ac.uk/stacc">Cloud Computing</a>.</li>

<li>In general I am always on the lookout for good PhD students 
&mdash; see my <a href=
"research/">research page</a> for more. Funding is currently
available for qualified students (including overseas students) &mdash; 
see the <a href=
"http://www.sicsa.ac.uk/graduate-academy/prize-studentships/sicsa-prize-studentships/">
SICSA</a> pages. Note that I do <b>not</b> have funding
for overseas undergraduate internships &mdash; the numerous 
requests that I receive for these are ignored.</li>

<li>We hold regular <a href="http://scone.cs.st-andrews.ac.uk/">SCONE</a>
(SCOttish Networking Event) meetings for anyone who is interested in networking and systems. Please consider coming to our
next meeting &mdash; Edinburgh, <a href=
"http://scone.cs.st-andrews.ac.uk/wiki/Meeting12032009">
12 March</a>.</li>

<li>I am responsible for publicity and recruitment in our School.
If you are thinking about studying Computer Science at St Andrews, 
take a look at the relevant <a href=
"http://www.cs.st-andrews.ac.uk/prospective-ug">School webpages</a>
and please consider <a href=
"http://www.st-andrews.ac.uk/admissions/VisitingtheUniversity/">visiting
us</a>.</li>

<li>I am currently involved with the following events. Please
consider submitting something if you can.

<ul>
<li>Programme Committee, <a href="http://www.mmsys.org/">Multimedia Systems 2010</a></li>
<li>Steering/Programme Committee, <a href="http://www-poleia.lip6.fr/~netgames2009/">NetGames 2009</a></li>
<li>Programme Committee, <a href="http://conferences.sigcomm.org/sigcomm/2009/workshops/wosn/index.php">WOSN 2009</a></li>
<li>Programme Committee, <a href="http://hotplanetconf.net/">HotPlanet</a></li>
<li>Steering/Programme Committee, <a href="http://www.extremecom.org/">ExtremeCom</a></li>
<li>Publicity Chair, <a href="http://www.mobiquitous.org/">Mobiquitous 2009</a></li>
<li>Publicity Chair, <a href="http://www.nossdav.org/2009/">NOSSDAV 2009</a></li>
</ul>
</li>

</ul>

